The potato is a remarkable thing: it contains an extraordinary variety of nutrients, more potassium than a banana, and hearty amounts of Vitamin C. It can be fried, baked, mashed, roasted, or stewed. But as we all know, with this mod its main use is no longer Schnapps alone.
Eat your veggies each and every day! Rich in micronutrients, these staples should be part of everyone's diet for a healthy and prosperous life!
Contrary to recent changes in modern legislation, the only use of these plants is for their high fibre content in the manufacture of basic textiles and ropes.
With wheat, one can make both bread and beer: a complete diet, as far as certain nations in the Old World are concerned.
Once confined to the gardens of wealthy monestaries, this plant is now needed in large quantities for its preservative ingredients to spice up your workers' favourite drink.
A variety of herbs are grown on this farm for their beautiful colours and aromatic scent! A wonderful ingredient to round off any dish! Definitely not to be missed in any kitchen.
A little dull looking green and violet grapes. These recent vintages from the Old World will delight your Landowners' souls!

Madder is a traditional dyeing plant. From ancient times until the discovery of synthetic dyes, this plant played a central role in the process of dyeing cloth. Its intense red colour was often used as a substitute for the very expensive tyrian purple, but does not achieve its unique hue.

An Apple a day keeps the Doctor away! Choose one of more than 20000 varieties! Apples can be used to make pretty much anything that tastes good: from apple strudel to fine cider. A true all-rounder!
The Tradtional Brewery can produce any beverage produced in the Old World World, so long as you have unlocked the need. Select a beverage, then click the 'Begin Brewing' button to commence!

Cider is a drink that is thousands of years old and was already very popular with the Celts. Preserved by yeast fermentation, the sweet apple juice turns into a fruity, tangy refreshment for hot days.
The intense flavour of these sun-ripened grapes produces a unique bouquet. Maturing the young wine in solid oak barrels further refines its tart flavour.
An overview of all available Traditional Breweries
Using better tools, this module will enable the preparation of venison from hunted game.
Skilled carpenters can craft a variety of products from one of the most versatile materials of the pre-industrial age: Wood

The most basic versions of modern engineering marvels are made in these workshops from suitable hardwood species. The use of tools will enable your workers to increase their productivity and push production figures to new heights!

One of the first storage solutions in modern human history. More durable and spacious than pottery, Barrels can store almost any type of product for later use. Barrels are also essential for refining certain drinks into delicious concoctions.
These veneers, carved from precious woods, are handmade by skilled craftsmen. Wood veneers are used in the most luxurious applications to amaze the most ardent of art lovers.

This framework is just the beginning of something huge! Chassis are essential to the ever growing development of personal transport. And finally, those bumps will no longer ruin your buttocks on long journeys.

Consumption of goods will be lowered by 5% and happiness will increase by 5.

Supplying your Landowners with certain Happiness Needs provides you with additional Influence
Landowners require farmers to pay a tithe for using their land.
Landowners enact the obligation for farmers working on their grounds to pay a tithe in return for their provision of arable land.
A social welfare system supports those unable to work in an industrialized society.
To support the burden of the working class in an increasingly industrialized society, a social welfare system provides security for those left behind or incapable of working.
Home workshops on rural farms significantly increases the availability of consumption products for the lower strata.
By introduction of home workshops in rural farms the availability of certain consumption goods for the lower strata can be increased by a good margin.
Hunting rights will be only handed out to royal individuals.
Shifting the right to hunt from the local farmers to a more selective group of highly trained individuals with superior tools results in increased rare outputs of hunting cabines.
Impressed by industrialization, landowners seek to modernize their workshops but, lacking machinery and power, increase output by intensifying human labor.

Impressed by the development of more industrial processes in the cities factories, the landowners want to modernize their artisan workshops as well. Since they can’t supply sufficient machinery and power to the workshops though, they brute force more output with increased use of human resources.

This gate is just the beginning of a magnificent Manor Park! Expand it by building Ornaments from this category or certain vanilla ones in the vicinity of your Manors.

Each Ornament reduces the Landowners' need for "Manor Park" by a small amount. Build enough Ornaments in the vicinity of the Manors to reduce the requirement by 100%, resulting in the fulfilment of your Landowners' needs.
The Queen informs you, that she can now assign more Aristocratic Titles to your citizens.
The Queen will grant you with more Aristocratic Titles in exchange for a certain amount of money.
Additional Cultivation Area for the Orangery
Providing your Orangery workers with sophisticated tools to trim the branches of their citrus trees will increase the overall yields.
This gate is just the beginning of a magnificent Manor Park! Expand it by building Ornaments around it.
Horse Ploughs increase a farm's cultivation area and productivity while reducing the workforce requirement while consuming Horses and Tools.
Landowners are securing profitable "extra" deals with Traders in deviation from the officially negotiated trade agreement.
Landowners are securing profitable "extra" deals with Traders in deviation from the officially negotiated trade agreement, securing additional Tradelicenses in the process.
Proper Handling Piers and advancements in packaging increase the efficiency of Import Piers.
Proper Handling Piers and advancements in packaging increase the efficiency of Import Piers, making your stored imported goods last longer.
Investors and Landowners consume 5% less of every good.

All Administration Buildings come with a standard debuff. Buildings outside of the Administration range will not function properly. Move them inside the radius of the Administration or increase its range by assigning more Landowner workforce (Press Shift+C for the second UI) to get a counter-buff that offsets the initial debuff.

With increasing numbers, Landowners will start to invest in the construction and expansion of cultural institutions, which will increase the effectiveness of your exhibitions and raise the attractiveness of your islands level by level.
WIDESPREAD USE OF DUNG AND HORSE-DRAWN PLOUGHS REVOLUTIONISES AGRICULTURE

Farmers are baffled after introduction of newly developed horse-drawn equipment. Yields are skyrocketing into oblivion. Soon, an interviewed farmer said, he could feed his village all by himself with the help of this new miricale steel plough! We expect [Participants Current Profile CompanyName] will once again chevron a path in the soil for others to follow.
Going to church every Sunday might be worth it at some point after all...
Lovely choral singing resounds from the cathedral during the pontifical mass
A considerable amount of goodies was donated to the collection this week
Your people went home revitalised by the sermon
Plan one of the biggest events this city has ever seen! The Municipal Theatre can host a variety of events to entertain your high class!
Will Mr Holmes manage to convict the culprit again this time with his newly invented method of deduction? Find out in the latest performance at your state theatre!
Mozart, Beethoven and Hayden! The most beautiful pieces in the world live on stage! No more talentless fiddling at home when you can spend money on professionals!
With calm and deliberation, the small balls are pushed over the clearly oversized table in planned strokes. Quiet in the audience please!
There's a lot of rattling and banging when the smartest engineers of our time present their new inventions and even demonstrate them live! Watch out: take cover!
The screen here is about thirty times bigger than on the projector at home! What a difference in picture quality!
Models from all over the world present the latest collections by your most gifted dressmakers!
Precious pieces of jewellery gleam under thick glass rails and paintings by famous artists can be admired on the walls. Even better than in your own home!
